National Security Advisor Susan E. Rice met with UN Special Envoy for Syria Staffan de Mistura to discuss the ongoing conflict in Syria. De Mistura provided an update on his recent regional consultations and briefing to the UN Security Council. Rice expressed the United States' support for a political solution to the conflict and emphasized their commitment to increasing support for the moderate Syrian opposition through a train and equip program. They also discussed measures that the United States and other partners could take to support de Mistura's efforts. Rice highlighted the United States' continued commitment to providing humanitarian assistance to those affected by the conflict.